<section class="section" id="projects" data-id="#03 / projekte">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="left">
        <span class="eyebrow">03 — Projekte</span>
        <h2>Was ich <em>so bau</em> &amp; veröffentliche.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="right">Open Source · PyPI · GitHub</div>
    </div>

    <div class="project-group">
      <div class="project-group-label"><span>Open-Source Tools</span></div>
      <div class="project-grid">
        <div class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-head">
            <div class="project-card-title">ollama-commit</div>
            <div class="project-badges">
              <a href="https://pypi.org/project/ollama-commit/" class="badge badge-pypi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyPI</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/dennisreichenberg/ollama-commit" class="badge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">Generiert automatisch aussagekräftige Git-Commit-Nachrichten mit lokalen LLMs über Ollama.</p>
          <div class="project-install">pip install ollama-commit</div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-head">
            <div class="project-card-title">local-rag</div>
            <div class="project-badges">
              <a href="https://pypi.org/project/ollama-local-rag/" class="badge badge-pypi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyPI</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/dennisreichenberg/local-rag" class="badge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">Lokales Retrieval-Augmented-Generation-System — Dokumente indexieren und mit lokalen LLMs befragen.</p>
          <div class="project-install">pip install ollama-local-rag</div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-head">
            <div class="project-card-title">devlog</div>
            <div class="project-badges">
              <a href="https://pypi.org/project/devlog/" class="badge badge-pypi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyPI</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/dennisreichenberg/devlog" class="badge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">AI-Entwicklertagebuch: Arbeit protokollieren, wöchentliche Zusammenfassungen und PR-Beschreibungen mit lokalen LLMs generieren.</p>
          <div class="project-install">pip install devlog</div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-head">
            <div class="project-card-title">model-manager</div>
            <div class="project-badges">
              <a href="https://pypi.org/project/model-manager/" class="badge badge-pypi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyPI</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/dennisreichenberg/model-manager" class="badge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">Einheitliche Kommandozeilen-Verwaltung für Ollama-Modelle: Auflisten, Herunterladen, Entfernen und Taggen.</p>
          <div class="project-install">pip install model-manager</div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-head">
            <div class="project-card-title">vllm-bench</div>
            <div class="project-badges">
              <span class="badge badge-soon">Coming soon</span>
              <a href="https://github.com/dennisreichenberg/vllm-bench" class="badge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">CLI-Benchmark für vLLM-Server-Performance: TTFT, Throughput und Inter-Token-Latenz messen.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-head">
            <div class="project-card-title">ollama-proxy</div>
            <div class="project-badges">
              <a href="https://pypi.org/project/ollama-proxy/" class="badge badge-pypi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyPI</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/dennisreichenberg/ollama-proxy" class="badge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">Unified OpenAI-kompatibler API-Router für Ollama- und vLLM-Backends.</p>
          <div class="project-install">pip install ollama-proxy</div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-head">
            <div class="project-card-title">agent-runner</div>
            <div class="project-badges">
              <a href="https://pypi.org/project/agent-runner/" class="badge badge-pypi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PyPI</a>
              <a href="https://github.com/dennisreichenberg/agent-runner" class="badge" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">CLI-Agent-Loop-Framework mit Tool-Use für lokale LLMs.</p>
          <div class="project-install">pip install agent-runner</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/tools" class="all-tools-link">Alle Tools und Stacks ansehen <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="project-group">
      <div class="project-group-label"><span>Weitere Projekte</span></div>
      <div class="project-grid-wide">
        <div class="project-card-wide">
          <div class="project-num">01 / Enterprise</div>
          <div class="project-card-title">Internes ERP-Modul</div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">Erweiterung des firmeninternen ERP-Systems mit Automatisierungen für Auftragsverarbeitung und Berichtswesen.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card-wide">
          <div class="project-num">02 / Pipeline</div>
          <div class="project-card-title">Automatisiertes Datenpipeline-Tool</div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">ETL-Pipeline zur automatisierten Verarbeitung und Bereinigung von Produktions- und Vertriebsdaten.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card-wide">
          <div class="project-num">03 / Infrastruktur</div>
          <div class="project-card-title">Self-hosted KI-Infrastruktur</div>
          <p class="project-card-desc">Aufbau und Betrieb einer lokalen KI-Infrastruktur mit Ollama, vLLM und Open WebUI auf eigener Hardware.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .all-tools-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 10px 18px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .all-tools-link::before {
    content: "$ ";
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .all-tools-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--surface-2);
  }
  .all-tools-link .arrow {
    transition: transform 0.15s ease;
  }
  .all-tools-link:hover .arrow {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }
  .badge-soon {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    border: 1px dashed var(--muted);
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
